metadata.name: Beyond the Earthly Mind
metadata.description:
"Imagination is more important than knowledge" 
(A. Einstein)
This illustration shows what can be beyond the earthly mind. Somewhere far away, in other star systems, other galaxies, or perhaps in worlds invisible to us.
With the help of our imagination, we can create these worlds that will live through the fine arts for many generations of mankind.
Very detailed work with many lines and elements.
Primary source - physical art on A2 paper (594x420mm) created with ink liners
original size 5480 x 7736 px
